/**
 * Handles writing characters to the screen.
 * The text screen is divided into 23 rows (0..22), each containing
 * 64 columns (0..63).
 * Each row is 11 pixels high (including 1 space pixel), and 8 pixels
 * wide (including 2 space pixels).
 */
